                ""
            ],
            "correct_response": [
                [
                    "3"
                ]
            ],
            "solution": "<div><B>Solution: <br>Correct\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAnswer : <b>3</B>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>91 = 9K + 1<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t92 = 9K + 2<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t93 = 9K + 3<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t94 = 9K + 4<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t95 = 9K + 5<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t96 + 9k + 6<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t97 = 9K + 7<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t98 = 9K + 8<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t99 = 9K + 9<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tIf we take 1 number of the form (9K + 1) then we can not have numbers of the form (9K +\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t8); similarly<br><br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t9K + 1 or 9K + 8<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t9K + 2 or 9K + 7<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t9K + 3 or 9K + 6<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\t9K + 4 or 9K + 5<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAnd, one of 9K + 9<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\twhere K = 10, 11, \u2026, 19;<br>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAns.: 41.</div></div>"
