            "solution": "<div><B>Solution: <br>Correct\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tAnswer : <b>7</B>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<div>It is similar to the case of circular motion where 2 runners are running in opposite\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tdirection. Hence number of meeting\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t\tpoints is (3 + 4) = 7.</div></div>"
